title: Ep. - 393 - PROFESSIONAL TENNIS PLAYER MARDY FISH REAL HOUSEWIVES OF SALT LAKE CITY REVIEW
description:
Former professional tennis player Mardy Fish from Untold, a five-part Netflix docuseries event that brings fresh eyes to tales from the wide world of sports. Under pressure to continue a winning tradition in American tennis, Mardy Fish faced mental health challenges that changed his life on and off the court.

 

Legal commentator Emily D. Baker helps Kate review the season premiere of Bravo’s Real Housewives of Salt Lake City.
